         ${misc:Depends},
         ${python:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Experimental MAPI (Exchange/Outlook) server
 This is a plugin for Samba 4 that adds server-side support for the MAPI
 protocol that is used by Microsoft Outlook and Exchange.

