Package: openchange-notification
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Openchange notifications daemon
 This package contains a daemon that receive messages published by dovecot
 openchange plugin, registers the message in the user mailbox and push a
 notification for openchange mapiproxy to notify the user.
